{"tid":1531220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好流水式塔黨鐵呀","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T07:08:55.000Z","uid":207197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9938bfcbb1fe163b658fd88ae73c95d11fa3fa16","tid":1531220,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"香港人平時咁熱愛番工<br />\n叫擺工? 政府指住你黎笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都得個心支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一塞鐵又會比人屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家呢頭塔完鐵向A方向<br />\n發現漏左野係屋企又要塔番B方向<br />\n又唔小心塔過龍塔番A方向<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個個打公仔/學生都咁大頭蝦<br />\n就會成班人塞死晒係黨鐵番唔到工/學架啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家千奇唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會搞到黨鐵好難做架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗想捉人都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係遊行集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都彩虹戰隊唔着黑衫<br />\n唔通<span style=\"color: red;\">大頭蝦犯法咩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人就一向燥底同閪架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係呢d日子<br />\n太逼會比人屌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">塔黨鐵要企鬆d</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就大家都舒服 <br />\n又可以避免鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲小小先番到學/工姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace34070aa8e39512c50bb62578b86ee1125e2e4","tid":1531220,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好咁做"},{"pid":"8b7aee9c742428bb878bc6f5ec061fa735f50c3a","tid":1531220,"uid":257422,"